# ── Forensic Image Analysis Engine Configuration ──

# Google Gemini API Key (Required for AI Investigation)
# Get your free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Groq API Key (Optional Fallback for Fallback LLM support)
# Get your key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Notes:
# - Rename this file to .env before running.
# - Ensure GEMINI_API_KEY is present for primary RAG functionality.
